We already have the profit margin since we previously calculated and we know it is a ratio so it is not affected by the change of currency as stated earlier.

$$ \begin{aligned}
\text{Net (income/loss)} & = {\$395,183}\cdot\text{-0.092}\\

& =\boxed{ -\$36,504}
\end{aligned}$$

Now we know that the company's net loss in USD is  **-$36,504**.
